game.name: Swimwear Fashion
game.description:
The weather is extremely lovely and your character has decided to spend some time at beach. Yes, today is her holiday, so the girl put all her other important works aside and get ready to have fun at beach throughout the day. But, the problem is that she does not have an idea what type of swimwear she should wear to make her holiday at beach enjoyable. Will you help her out right away? Join Swimwear Fashion game and be prepared to help the girl pick up some cool and trendy swimwear!
A big beach dressing competition will take place today. So, being a fashionista, it will be your responsibility to sort out this puzzle by exploring all the dress options the girl contains in her wardrobe in this brand new dressing game. Common ladies! Your good knowledge about the fashion world will lead you towards the selection of a nice swimming outfit. Give your girl a stylish top combined with a matching bottom! Explore from different types of accessories like elegant jewelry items, some sun glasses and a beach bag!
Feel free to complete her look with a messy bun or beach waves hairstyle in this html5 kids dress up game! Do your best to make your girl as stunning as you can and allow her to have fun at the beach in the best possible manner! The sexier beach looks she has, the happier moments she will be able to take home during with her. Good luck to create the best beach look you have ever produced! Enjoy the best beach games online on atmegame.com, no download required!
